<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>DT 466 / DT 570 / HT 570 Service Manual - 2004 Emissions with EGR - Diamond Logic&#8482; Engine Brake -
        Reconditioning
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Reconditioning</title>
        <svcproc graphiccount="0">
            <title>Brake Assembly Components</title>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>If for any reason the valve cover is removed, verify the six brake piston locknuts are tight.
                        If found loose, verify and reset brake lash as required.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>When the high-pressure oil manifold equipped with a brake is removed for reasons other than
                        cylinder head reconditioning, inspect the contact surfaces which include brake actuator piston
                        face and top of valve bridge at six locations. Inspect for evidence of pitting and material
                        transfer deformation. Replace as necessary. Polished surfaces are acceptable.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <para>The following items are available as service parts as required after diagnostic testing. See engine
                diagnostic manual for further information about appropriate tests.
            </para>
            <seqlist>
                <item>
                    <para>Brake shutoff valve assembly</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>ICP sensor with O-ring</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>BCP sensor with O-ring</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Plug, M10 (3)</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Brake housing bolt, M8 x 90 (12)</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Plug assembly, M12 (2)</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>High-pressure supply to rail O-ring</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Oil pressure relief valve</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Brake actuator piston assembly</para>
                </item>
            </seqlist>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
